title: Bobby Behind The Scenes Of AMC’s + Raymundo’s Finance Tells Her Side + Kalie Shorr Stops By With A Big Announcement
itunes:title: Bobby Behind The Scenes Of AMC’s + Raymundo’s Finance Tells Her Side + Kalie Shorr Stops By With A Big Announcement
description:
Bobby talks about what it was like presenting at the ACM’s last night with all the COVID precautions. He also give his opinion on the split Entertainer of the Year award. We talk with Raymundo’s fiancé about all the crazy stories he's shared with us this week. Plus, Kalie Shorr stops by the studio and performs for us! Bobby announces her new podcast called, 'Too Much To Say' with Kalie Shore. It's available NOW!
